         <abstract encodinganalog="520$a" label="Abstract">Consists primarily of letters from
				Aurelia Schrober Plath, 1906-1994, to Mary Ann Montgomery. Interfiled among those
				letters are carbon copies of Dr. Montgomery's letters to Mrs. Plath. Other
				correspondents present in the collection are Bill and Hillary Clinton and other
				White House officials, and poet Robert Lax. A folder of miscellaneous letters
